<HEADLINE>
<P>
DELIVERING THE NEW YEAR BABY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
To use such a precious gift as birth and turn it into a trivial contest of 
who's first leaves me to question the ethics of not only Dr. Turner Jr., but of 
the parents of newborn Myra Palmer. 
</P>
<P>
Dr. Turner stated "I knew God had a hand in it." If God had a hand in it he 
would have used it to slap Turner's face and bring him to his senses! 
</P>
<P>
JOEY R. KRYS 
</P>
<P>
Orange Parks Acres 
</P>
