<P>
Buchanan's article ended the year on a shrill note, if not a high one. 
</P>
<P>
He states that the diplomats in the Organization of American States and those 
in the United Nations condemn our invasion of Panama, but privately agree with 
our actions. If this is true (an unprovable allegation), why? Could they fear 
