FAITH IN MICHAEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bravo to Dennis Hunt ("Times' Critics' Best Albums of the '80s," Dec. 24). 
</P>
<P>
Of the 12 "critics" who chose their favorite albums, only Hunt included George 
Michael's "Faith." 
</P>
<P>
Beside being one of the best-selling records of this decade, it gave George 
Michael three American Music Awards and a Grammy for album of the year, it was 
the No. 1 album for several weeks and it had several No. 1 singles. 
</P>
<P>
I think it's about time people started rating records on public response and 
not solely on critical acclaim. 
</P>
