<TEXT>
<P>
Field judge Pat Mallette had to leave the Minnesota Vikings-San Francisco 49ers 
playoff game in the first quarter Saturday after colliding with a player on Joe 
Montana's 72-yard touchdown pass play to Jerry Rice. 
</P>
