their final night in Moscow. Reuter; Photo, ON TOUR IN THE U.S.S.R. Full house 
-- Leningrad's 4,000-seat October Hall was typical of venues visited by Jenkins 
Dance Company, ODC/San Francisco on overlapping tour of Soviet cities. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
